msg: CAMEL-4773: Dynamic Router, Routing Slip and other EIPs which accept an expression for endpoints, should cater for bean endpoints separated by comma. Where a bean endpoint uses method name parameter using parantheses with comma included. ObjectHelper.createIterator needs to honor this, when its iterating a String value.
